params._streamer: The address of the streamer to unsubscribe from

getAvailableTokenEarnings(address).details: Get available token earnings for withdrawal

returns.endTime: The end time of the subscription
returns.startTime: The start time of the subscription

getTotalAvailableEarnings().details: Get total available earnings (ETH + tokens) for a streamer

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

params._duration: Additional duration to add in seconds
params._streamer: The address of the streamer to renew subscription for

params._amount: The amount of tokens to pay

params._streamer: The address of the streamer to subscribe to

params._amount: The amount of tokens to pay
params._duration: Duration of the subscription in seconds (min 1 day, max 365 days)
